comments: Soooooo nice!! And an easy A forsure!! Wish she taught more subjects, she\'s very knowledgable in her field. Warning this class might turn you into a vegetarian

She is one of the best teachers i\'ve ever had, it is a pleasure to rate her. She had us do a lot of group discussion, even had us sit outside for a socratic discussion once, it was cool. I missed a few days but still got an A, she\'s the best.
She\'s an awesome teacher. Very caring, nice, and passionate about what she teaches. Used the book often during class and you need to skim through it for the tests. All in all, she\'s great.

If you know anything about psych before taking this class, you don\'t really learn anything new; but the class is an easy grade and she is a great teacher. Always goes over what is on the exams and not a lot of erroneous work or studying. Really pleasant and friendly, easy going and genuinely interested in her student\'s lives. Good class, easy A
shes so nice!! and so easy. do not need a book at alll.dont even bother going to class ;D
Very friendly and approachable. Runs a pretty fun, exciting class. Provides lots of variety and learning opportunities in class time. She\'s very enthusiastic about the subject matter. Good teacher.
such a sweet woman. is a yoga/vegan lover and is very respectful towards students. take her class and study the book a little for exams. you\'ll do great!
